# {{intransitive}} To [[stay]]; to [[continue]] in a place; to remain [[stable]] or [[fixed]] in some state or condition; to be left. {{defdate|First attested from around (1150 to 1350).}}<ref name=SOED/>
#* {{RQ:Authorized Version|1 Corinthians|7|20}}
